    "All research procedures were conducted in accordance with the Declaration of Helsinki.",
    "Ethical approval was granted by the Ethics Committee of the Technical University of Munich (reference number 2024-98-S-CB) and the Ethics Committee of Westfalen-Lippe (reference number 2024-157-b-S).",
    "The tissue samples used were from an existing biobank and were not collected specifically for this study.",
    "As this was a retrospective data collection and the data were fully anonymized, informed consent was not obtained in consultation with the local ethics committee.",
    "No compensation was provided as there was no direct participant involvement in the study."
